<template>
	<svg
		class="editorial"
		xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
		xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
		viewBox="0 24 150 28 "
		preserveAspectRatio="none"
	>
		<defs>
			<path
				id="gentle-wave"
				d="M-160 44c30 0 
    58-18 88-18s
    58 18 88 18 
    58-18 88-18 
    58 18 88 18
    v44h-352z"
			/>
		</defs>
		<g class="parallax1">
			<use xlink:href="#gentle-wave" x="50" y="1" fill="#2b29cc" />
		</g>
		<g class="parallax2">
			<use xlink:href="#gentle-wave" x="50" y="0" fill="#1917d9" />
		</g>
		<g class="parallax3">
			<use xlink:href="#gentle-wave" x="50" y="1" fill="#0d64b3" />
		</g>
		<g class="parallax4">
			<use xlink:href="#gentle-wave" x="50" y="2" fill="#16537e" />
		</g>
	</svg>
</template>

<script>
export default {
	name: "Home",
	props: {
		msg: String,
	},
	methods: {
		greet() {
			console.log("Hello");
		},
	},
};
</script>

<style>
body {
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0;
	background-color: #03396c;
}

.editorial {
	display: block;
	width: 100%;
	height: 30px;
	max-height: 30px;
	margin: 0;
	z-index: 5;
	bottom: 0;
	position: absolute;
	left: 0px;
	float: left;
}

.parallax1 > use {
	animation: move-forever1 10s linear infinite;
	&:nth-child(1) {
		animation-delay: -4s;
	}
}
.parallax2 > use {
	animation: move-forever2 8s linear infinite;
	&:nth-child(1) {
		animation-delay: -4s;
	}
}
.parallax3 > use {
	animation: move-forever3 6s linear infinite;
	&:nth-child(1) {
		animation-delay: -4s;
	}
}
.parallax4 > use {
	animation: move-forever4 4s linear infinite;
	&:nth-child(1) {
		animation-delay: -4s;
	}
}
@keyframes move-forever1 {
	0% {
		transform: translate(85px, 0%);
	}
	100% {
		transform: translate(-90px, 0%);
	}
}
@keyframes move-forever2 {
	0% {
		transform: translate(-90px, 0%);
	}
	100% {
		transform: translate(85px, 0%);
	}
}
@keyframes move-forever3 {
	0% {
		transform: translate(85px, 0%);
	}
	100% {
		transform: translate(-90px, 0%);
	}
}
@keyframes move-forever4 {
	0% {
		transform: translate(-90px, 0%);
	}
	100% {
		transform: translate(85px, 0%);
	}
}
</style>
